%% 关键流程时序 v2.2.0 · stage66
sequenceDiagram
  participant U as 用户/管理员
  participant N as nginx
  participant A as FastAPI
  participant R as refresh_pipeline
  participant P as profit 分整数
  participant D as SQLite

  Note over A,R: 日更 ScheduleLoop / 一键更新 = do_full
  A->>R: do_full / generate
  R->>D: build_std + 重放调整
  R->>P: summary_from_conn Decimal 分
  R->>A: publish summary/fragments/views<br/>不预装 user_html

  Note over U,A: 手填保存 = 增量重算
  U->>N: POST /api/manual
  N->>A: 
  A->>D: set_manual
  A->>R: recompute rebuild_std=False<br/>源指纹未变跳过 std
  R->>P: summary 重算
  R->>A: publish

  Note over U,A: 调整 = 重建 std + 重放
  U->>A: POST /api/adjust
  A->>R: recompute rebuild_std=True

  Note over U,A: 导出 PNG 按需装配
  U->>A: GET /export.png
  A->>P: assemble_export_html 现场
  A-->>U: PNG
